fields.value: NMR data for 8-prenylapigenin, bavachinin, licochalcone C and Abyssinone II

dsDescriptionValue.value: This folder contains the NMR datasets ( 1D 1H, 2D COSY, HSQC, HMBC) related to the structural description of 8-prenylapigenin (8PA),  the NMR data associated with the structure analysis of bavachalcone mistakenly sold as 8-prenylapigenin, as well as the structure verification of co-isolated abyssinone II and licochalcone C.

contributorName.value: Dr. David C. Lankin (University of Illinois at Chicago)
Dr. Charlotte Simmler (University of Illinois at Chicago)

files.description: This file contains  (1)  the raw NMR data (1D and 2D, jdx and Bruker fid) related to the structure verification of.4' O-Methylbroussochalcone B (Pubchem ID: 5321765), this compound isomerized readily in the NMR tube in DMSO-d6 into its flavanone isomer (syn. 7-O-Methylbavachin; Bavachinin A, Pubchem ID 10337211) (2) the NMR parameter file (HIFSA) enabling the accurate description of coupling constants for both isomers,  (3) the annotated 1H and 13C (only for bavachinin) NMR spectra in DMSO-d6. 1H NMR data from 2015 show primarily the chalcone, all the NMR data acquired in 2017 show correlations for the  more abundant flavanone.
files.label: 4'OmethylbroussochalconeB_BavachininA_NMRdata_HIFSA_DMSOD6_600_900MHz.zip

files.description: This file contains (1) the raw NMR data (1D and 2D, jdx and Bruker fid) related to the structure verification of Licochalcone C (Pubchem ID: 9840805), (2) the NMR parameter file (HIFSA) enabling the accurate description of coupling constants (3) the annotated 1H and 13C NMR spectra in DMSO-d6.
